      <text x="350" y="112" fill="#fca5a5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="800">Elastizität ✗</text>
      <text x="350" y="138" fill="#e4e4e7" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Angebot passt</text>
